{"word":"H4685 - מָצֹוד - mâtsôwd - maw-tsode' - Bulwark","slug":"H4685","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָצֹוד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâtsôwd"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-tsode'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bulwark"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E6;&#x05D3;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05E6;&#x05D5;&#x05D3;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05E6;&#x05D5;&#x05D3; - ma&#x0302;tso&#x0302;d  m<sup>e</sup>tso&#x0302;da&#x0302;h  m<sup>e</sup>tso&#x0302;da&#x0302;h</b> - <i>maw-tsode', mets-o-daw', mets-o-daw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6679\">H6679</a>; a <i>net</i> (for <i>capturing</i> animals or fishes); also (by interchange for <a href=\"#/H4679\">H4679</a>) a <i>fastness</i> or (besieging) <i>tower: - </i>bulwark, hold, munition, net, snare."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4679\">H4679</a>, <a href=\"#/H4686\">H4686</a>, <a href=\"#/H6679\">H6679</a>, <a href=\"#/H6718\">H6718</a>, <a href=\"#/H6719\">H6719</a>"}]}